params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.path
params.description: Optional. The directory's full path including directory name, relative to the workspace root. If left unset, the workspace root is used.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. Maximum number of paths to return. The server may return fewer items than requested. If unspecified, the server will pick an appropriate default.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. Page token received from a previous QueryDirectoryContents call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to QueryDirectoryContents must match the call that provided the page token.
